                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8512" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0250</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1015 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">责任与担当：中信建投沉着应对之道</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Liability and responsibility: CSC&#39;s calm response</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">赵自强，魏宇航，蒋舒恒</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南京师范大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中信建投证券股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贸易与金融业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">注册制；先行赔付；内部控制；风险管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Registration system; Pay first; Internal control; Risk management</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">合法有序的资本市场不仅仰仗于监管机构的有效监管，更离不开保荐机构勤勉尽责的工作态度。当发行人涉嫌欺诈发行、信息披露违规时，作为证券发行上市的保荐机构，证券公司难辞其咎。在此情况下，证券公司如何有效应对以摆脱困境成为一个值得深思的议题，而对证券公司进行有效整改、避免此次事件的发生更是成为压实“看门人”责任的必要途径。在新《证券法》出台、全面实施注册制的背景之下，本案例讲述了中信建投保荐紫晶存储上市的详细过程，而在紫晶存储欺诈发行上市被认定之后，叙述了中信建投会同其他中介机构设立先行赔付专项基金及基金运作的始末，展现了中信建投在紫晶存储事件爆发后的积极应对之路。以紫晶存储欺诈发行、中信建投积极设立先行赔付专项基金为叙述重点，本案例引导学生思考中信建投在本次事件中反映出的公司内部控制的缺陷，接着从风险管理的角度来帮助学生了解其积极设立先行赔付专项基金的动因。基于投行业务内部控制原则，本案例进一步引导学生探究中信建投完善内部控制的可行路径，以期为保荐机构完善内部控制提供一定借鉴。最后，本案例基于利益相关者的角度，使学生思考先行赔付制度对中信建投和资本市场内部控制建设的意义，以期为资本市场平稳健康发展提供可实行之法。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">A legal and orderly capital market not only relies on the effective supervision of regulatory agencies, but also inseparable from the diligent and conscientious work attitude of sponsor agencies. When an issuer is suspected of fraudulent issuance and information disclosure violations, as a sponsor for securities issuance and listing, the securities company is blamed. Under this circumstance, how securities companies can effectively respond to the situation has become a topic worth pondering, and effectively rectifying securities companies and avoiding this incident has become a necessary way to consolidate the responsibility of the &quot;gatekeeper&quot;. Against the background of the promulgation of the new Securities Law and the full implementation of the registration system, this case describes the detailed process of CSC Construction Investment&#39;s sponsorship of Amethyst Storage for listing. After the fraudulent issuance and listing of Amethyst Storage was found, it describes the beginning and end of CSC Construction Investment&#39;s establishment of a special fund for advance compensation and its operation with other intermediaries, demonstrating CSC Construction Investment&#39;s proactive response after the outbreak of the Amethyst Storage incident. Focusing on the fraudulent issuance of Amethyst Storage and CSC Construction Investment&#39;s active establishment of a special fund for advance compensation, this case guides students to think about the shortcomings of the company&#39;s internal control reflected by CSC Construction Investment in this incident, and then helps students from the perspective of risk management. Understand their motivation for actively establishing a special fund for advance compensation. Based on the internal control principles of investment banking business, this case further guides students to explore feasible paths for CSC Construction Investment to improve internal control, in order to provide certain reference for recommendation institutions to improve internal control. Finally, based on the perspective of stakeholders, this case allows students to think about the significance of the advance compensation system to CSC Construction Investment and the construction of internal control in the capital market, in order to provide practical methods for the stable and healthy development of the capital market.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《内部控制与风险管理》、《内部控制》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">证券发行相关法律法规；COSO内部控制五要素；COSO-ERM企业风险管理整合框架；投行业务内部控制原则；利益相关者理论。</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
